msgctxt "EmmComponent|"
msgid ""
"Only available when contrasts are specified. To correct for multiple "
"comparison testing and avoid Type I errors, different methods for correcting "
"the p-value are available:"
msgstr ""
"Hanya tersedia ketika kontras ditentukan. Untuk mengoreksi untuk beberapa "
"uji perbandingan dan menghindari galat Jenis I, metode berbeda untuk "
"mengoreksi nilai-p tersedia:"

msgctxt "ExportFreq|"
msgid ""
"Save the residuals of the most complex model as a new column in the data "
"file."
msgstr ""
"Simpan residu dari model lebih kompleks sebagai kolom baru dalam berkas data."

msgctxt "ExportFreq|"
msgid ""
"Choose the type of residual to be appended. Raw residuals are simply the "
"differences between observation and model prediction, standardized residuals "
"divide each residual by an estimate of its standard deviation (using "
"rstandard()), whereas studentized residuals divide each residual by an "
"unbiased estimate of its standard deviation computed by refitting the model "
"without that observation  (using rstudent())."
msgstr ""
"Pilih jenis redisu untuk ditambahkan. Residu mentah secara sederhana "
"perbedaan antara observasi dan prediksi model, residu terstandardisasi "
"membagikan setiap redisu oleh estimasi deviasi standarnya (menggunakan "
"rstandard()), sementara residu terstudent membagikan setiap residu oleh "
"estimasi tidak bias deviasi standarnya dihitung dengan menyesuaikan ulang "
"model tanpa observasi itu  (menggunakan rstudent())."

msgctxt "ExportFreq|"
msgid ""
"Save the predictions of the most complex model as a new column in the data "
"file"
msgstr ""
"Simpan prediksi untuk model lebih kompleks sebagai kolom baru dalam berkas "
"data"

msgctxt "GlmInputComponent|"
msgid "Qualitative variables, such as gender and group memberships."
msgstr "Variabel kualitatif, seperti keanggotaan kelamin dan grup."

msgctxt "GlmInputComponent|"
msgid ""
"Prior weights of the model. Mandatory when the binomial family is selected. "
"In this case, the name changes to total Number of Trials, and the dependent "
"variable now refers to the proportion of success (between 0 and 1)."
msgstr ""
"Berat priori model. Wajib ketika keluarga binomial dipilih. Dalam kasus ini, "
"nama diubah ke total Jumlah Percobaan, dan variabel dependen sekarang "
"merujuk ke proporsi keberhasilan (antara 0 dan 1)."

msgctxt "GlmResidualAnalysisPlotsComponent|"
msgid ""
"The following options provide visual diagnostics of the model assumptions "
"based on residuals."
msgstr ""
"Opsi berikut menyediakan diagnostik visual dari asumsi model berdasarkan "
"residu."

msgctxt "Correlation|"
msgid ""
"The Correlation analysis allows estimation of the population correlation, as "
"well as testing the null hypothesis that the population correlation between "
"pairs of variables equals 0. All possible pairs of the specified variables "
"are analyzed.\n"
msgstr ""
"Analisis Korelasi mengizinkan estimasi dari korelasi populasi, serta menguji "
"hipotesis null bahwa korelasi populasi antara pasangan variabel sama dengan "
"0. Semua pasangan variabel yang memungkinkan dari variabel tertentu "
"dianalisiskan.\n"

msgctxt "Correlation|"
msgid "Assumptions (Pearson's rho)"
msgstr "Asumsu (rho Pearson)"

msgctxt "Correlation|"
msgid "Input"
msgstr "Masukan"

msgctxt "Correlation|"
msgid "Variables to partial out in order to compute partial correlations."
msgstr "Variabel untuk parsial untuk menghitung korelasi parsial."

msgctxt "Correlation|"
msgid "The Fisher transformed effect size with standard error."
msgstr "Ukuran efek tertransformasi Fisher dengan galat standar."

msgctxt "Correlation|"
msgid "The number of complete observations for a given pair of variables."
msgstr "Jumlah observasi selesai untuk pasangan variabel diberikan."

msgctxt "Correlation|"
msgid ""
"Two-sided alternative hypothesis that the population correlation does not "
"equal 0."
msgstr ""
"Hipotesis alternatif dua sisi yang korelasi populasi tidak sama dengan 0."

msgctxt "Correlation|"
msgid ""
"One-sided alternative hypothesis that the population correlation is greater "
"than 0."
msgstr ""
"Hipotesis alternatif satu sisi yang korelasi populasi lebih besar dari 0."

msgctxt "Correlation|"
msgid ""
"Display the correlation coefficient(s) in the plot. This option also adds "
"the x% confidence interval(s) as specified in the Confidence Intervals "
"option."
msgstr ""
"Tampilkan koefisien korelasi dalam diagram. Opsi ini juga menambahkan x% "
"interval kepercayaan sebagai ditentukan di opsi Interval Kepercayaan."

msgctxt "Correlation|"
msgid ""
"Shapiro: Generalized Shapiro-Wilk test for multivariate normality by "
"Villasenor-Alva and Gonzalez-Estrada (2009), using the mvShapiroTest package."
msgstr ""
"Shapiro: Uji Shapiro-Wilk Terhasilkan untuk normalitas multivariat oleh "
"Villasenor-Alva dan Gonzalez-Estrada (2009), menggunakan paket mvShapiroTest."

msgctxt "Correlation|"
msgid ""
"Shapiro: For each possible combination of the selected variables, computes "
"the Shapiro-Wilk statistic to test the null hypothesis that the variable "
"pair has a bivariate normal distribution."
msgstr ""
"Shapiro: Untuk setiap kombinasi yang memungkinkan dari variabel terpilih, "
"menghitung statistik Shapiro-Wilk untuk menguji hipotesis null bahwa "
"pasangan variabel memiliki distribusi normal bivariat."

msgctxt "Correlation|"
msgid "Uses all complete observations for each individual pair of variables."
msgstr ""
"Menggunakan semua observasi lengkap untuk setiap pasangan individu variabel."

msgctxt "CorrelationBayesian|"
msgid "Assumptions (Pearson's rho)"
msgstr "Asumsi (rho Pearson)"

msgctxt "CorrelationBayesian|"
msgid "Assumptions (Kendall's tau)"
msgstr "Asumsi (tau Kendall)"

msgctxt "CorrelationBayesian|"
msgid "Input"
msgstr "Masukan"

msgctxt "CorrelationBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Two-sided alternative hypothesis that the population correlation does not "
"equal 0."
msgstr ""
"Hipotesis alternatif dua sisi yang korelasi populasi tidak sama dengan 0."

msgctxt "CorrelationBayesian|"
msgid ""
"One-sided alternative hypothesis that the population correlation is greater "
"than 0."
msgstr ""
"Hipotesis alternatif satu sisi yang korelasi populasi lebih besar dari 0."

msgctxt "CorrelationBayesian|"
msgid ""
"One-sided alternative hypothesis that the population correlation is lower "
"than 0."
msgstr ""
"Hipotesis alternatif satu sisi yang korelasi populasi lebih kecil dari 0."

msgctxt "CorrelationBayesian|"
msgid "Pearson's product moment correlation coefficient."
msgstr "Koefisien korelasi momen produk Pearson."

msgctxt "CorrelationBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Kendall's tau-b rank-order correlation coefficient to quantify the monotonic "
"association between two variables by comparing concordant and non-concordant "
"pairs."
msgstr ""
"Koefisien korelasi urutan-peringkat b-tau Kendall untuk mengukur asosiasi "
"monotonik antara dua variabel dengan membandingkan pasangan konkordan dan "
"non-konkordan."

msgctxt "CorrelationBayesian|"
msgid "Displays scatterplots for each specified pair of variables."
msgstr "Menampilkan diagram pencaran untuk setiap pasangan variabel tertentu."

msgctxt "CorrelationBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Displays the prior and posterior distribution of the correlation under the "
"alternative hypothesis for each specified pair of variables."
msgstr ""
"Menampilkan distribusi priori dan posterior dari korelasi di bawah hipotesis "
"alternatif untuk setiap pasangan variabel tertentu."

msgctxt "CorrelationBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Adds the median and the 95% credible interval of the posterior distribution "
"of the effect size."
msgstr ""
"Menambahkan median dan 95% interval kredibel dari distribusi posterior "
"ukuran efek."

msgctxt "CorrelationBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Adds the Bayes factor computed with the user-defined prior; adds a "
"probability wheel depicting the odds of the data under the null vs. "
"alternative hypothesis (Assuming null and alternative had equal probability "
"a priori)."
msgstr ""
"Menambahkan faktor Bayes dihitung dengan priori tertentukan pengguna; "
"menambahkan roda probabilitas menggambarkan ganjil data di bawah hipotesis "
"null vs. alternatif (Mengasumgikan null dan alternatif memiliki priori "
"probabilitas sama)."

msgctxt "CorrelationBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Displays the Bayes factor as a function of the width of the stretched beta "
"prior on the correlation for each specified pair of variables. The width of "
"the kappa prior is varied between 0 and 2."
msgstr ""
"Menampilkan faktor Bayes sebagai fungsi lebar dari priori beta yang "
"direntangkan pada korelasi untuk setiap pasangan variabel tertentu. Lebar "
"priori kappa divariasikan antara 0 dan 2."

msgctxt "CorrelationBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Adds the Bayes factor computed with the user-defined prior and the maximum "
"obtainable Bayes factor."
msgstr ""
"Menambahkan faktor Bayes yang dihitung dengan priori tertentukan pengguna "
"dan maksimum faktor Bayes yang dapat diperoleh."

msgctxt "CorrelationBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Displays the development of the Bayes factor as the data come in using the "
"user-defined prior for each specified pair of variables."
msgstr ""
"Menampilkan pengembangan faktor Bayes sebagai masuknya data menggunakan "
"priori tertentukan pengguna untuk setiap pasangan variabel tertentu."

msgctxt "CorrelationBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Adds the Bayes factor computed with the user-defined prior; adds a "
"probability wheel depicting the odds of the data under the null vs. "
"alternative hypothesis; shows the decisiveness of the evidence in terms of "
"Jeffreys' (1961) evidence categories."
msgstr ""
"Menambahkan faktor Bayes yang dihitung dengan priori tertentukan pengguna; "
"menambahkan roda probabilitas menggambarkan ganjil data di bawah hipotesis "
"null vs. alternatif; menampilkan ketegasan bukti dalam istilah kategori "
"bukti Jeffrey (1961)."

msgctxt "CorrelationBayesian|"
msgid "Uses all complete observations for each individual pair of variables."
msgstr ""
"Menggunakan semua observasi lengkap untuk setiap pasangan individu variabel."

msgctxt "CorrelationBayesian|"
msgid "Uses only complete cases across all variables."
msgstr "Menggunakan hanya kasus lengkap melintasi semua variabel."

msgctxt "GeneralizedLinearModel|"
msgid ""
"A generalized linear model (GLM) is a flexible extension of ordinary linear "
"regression. A widely used GLM is binary logistic regression. Generally "
"speaking, a GLM consists of a random component and a systematic component:\n"
msgstr ""
"Model linear umum (GLM) adalah ekstensi fleksibel dari regresi linear biasa. "
"GLM banyak digunakan adalah regreasi logistik biner. Secara umum, GLM "
"terdiri dari komponen acak dan komponen sistematis:\n"

msgctxt "GeneralizedLinearModel|"
msgid "Family and link"
msgstr "Keluarga dan tautan"

msgctxt "GeneralizedLinearModel|"
msgid "Assumptions"
msgstr "Asumsi"

msgctxt "GeneralizedLinearModel|"
msgid "Input"
msgstr "Masukan"

msgctxt "GeneralizedLinearModel|"
msgid ""
"All the independent variables and covariates that can be included in the "
"model."
msgstr ""
"Semua variabel independen dan kovariat yang dapat disertakan dalam model."

msgctxt "GeneralizedLinearModel|"
msgid ""
"A table providing information about the goodness-of-fit of the model, "
"including the corresponding fit statistic, the degree of freedom (df) and "
"the p-value."
msgstr ""
"Tabel menyediakan informasi tentang kesesuaian baik dari model, menyertakan "
"statistik kesesuaian sesuai, derajat kebebasan (df) dan nilai-p."

msgctxt "GeneralizedLinearModel|"
msgid ""
"Goodness-of-fit test based on deviance residuals, comparing the current "
"model against the saturated model."
msgstr ""
"Uji kesesuaian berdasarkan residu devians, membandingkan model saat ini "
"terhadap model tersaturasi."

msgctxt "GeneralizedLinearModel|"
msgid ""
"Goodness-of-fit test based on Pearson residuals, comparing the current model "
"against the saturated model."
msgstr ""
"Uji kesesuaian berdasarkan residu Pearson, membandingkan model saat ini "
"terhadap model tersaturasi."

msgctxt "GeneralizedLinearModel|"
msgid ""
"Provide the confidence intervals around the parameter estimates. The level "
"of the confidence intervals can be specified (default is 95%)."
msgstr ""
"Sediakan interval kepercayaan dikelilingi estimasi parameter. Tingkat dari "
"interval kepercayaan dapat ditentukan (bawaannya adalah 95%)."

msgctxt "GeneralizedLinearModel|"
msgid ""
" A table showing multicollinearity diagnostics of the model. The choices of "
"measures are as follows."
msgstr ""
" Tabel menampilkan diagnostik mulitkolinearitas model. Pemilihan pengukuran "
"adalah sebagai berikut."

msgctxt "GeneralizedLinearModel|"
msgid ""
"Set seeds: This gives you the possibility of setting a random seed for the "
"plots and tables based on quantile residuals in the Diagnostics Section. "
"Concretely, every time you generate a plot or a table based on quantile "
"residuals, you get a slightly different plot or table because one step in "
"the calculation of the quantile residuals involves drawing random values "
"from a distribution. By setting a random seed of your choice here (the "
"default is 1), you make sure that you can get exactly the same plots and "
"tables based on quantile residuals."
msgstr ""
"Atur benih: Ini memberikan Anda kemungkinan mengatur benih acak untuk "
"diagram dan tabel berdasarkan residu kuantil di Bagian Diagnostik. Secara "
"konkret, setiap waktu Anda menghasilkan diagram atau tabel berdasarkan "
"residu kuantil, Anda mendapatkan diagram atau tabel yang sedikit berbeda "
"karena satu langkah di perhitungan dari residu kuantil memperlibatkan "
"penggambaran nilai acak dari distribusi. Dengan mengatur benih acak dari "
"pemilihan Anda di sini (bawaannya adalah 1), Anda memastikan bahwa Anda "
"dapat mendapatkan secara tepat diagram dan tabel sama berdasarkan residu "
"kuantil."

msgctxt "RegressionLinear|"
msgid ""
"Linear regression allows the user to model a linear relationship between one "
"or more explanatory variable(s) (predictors) and a continuous dependent "
"(response) variable.\n"
msgstr ""
"Regresi logistik mengizinkan pengguna untuk memodelkan hubungan linear "
"antara satu atau lebih variabel penjelasan (prediktor) dan variabel dependen "
"berkelanjutan (tanggapan).\n"

msgctxt "RegressionLinear|"
msgid "Assumptions"
msgstr "Asumsi"

msgctxt "RegressionLinear|"
msgid "Dependent variable."
msgstr "Variabel dependen."

msgctxt "RegressionLinear|"
msgid ""
"Predictors are entered sequentially based on the criterion specified in "
"Stepping method criteria."
msgstr ""
"Prediktor dimasukkan secara sekuensial berdasarkan kriteria ditentukan di "
"kriteria metode Langkah."

msgctxt "RegressionLinear|"
msgid ""
"Predictors are entered sequentially based on the criterion specified in "
"Stepping method criteria; after each step, the least useful predictor is "
"removed."
msgstr ""
"Prediktor dimasukkan secara sekuensial berdasarkan kriteria ditentukan di "
"kriteria metode Langkah; setelah setiap langkah, prediktor tidak bermanfaat "
"dihapus."

msgctxt "RegressionLinear|"
msgid ""
"Continuous predictor variable(s). If ordinal variables are entered it is "
"assumed that their levels are equidistant. Hence, ordinal variables are "
"treated as continuous predictor variables."
msgstr ""
"Variabel prediktor kontinu. Jika variabel ordinal dimasukkan diasumsikan "
"bahwa tingkat mereka berjarak sama. Oleh karena itu, variabel ordinal "
"diperlakukan sebagai variabel prediktor kontinu."

msgctxt "RegressionLinear|"
msgid ""
"Model terms: The independent variables in the model. By default, all the "
"main effects of the specified independent variables are included in the "
"model. To include interactions, click multiple variables by holding the ctrl/"
"command button while clicking, and drag those into the Model Terms box."
msgstr ""
"Istilah model: Variabel independen dalam model. Secara bawaan, semua efek "
"utama dari variabel independen tertentu disertakan dalam model. Untuk "
"menyertakan interaksi, klik beberapa variabel dengan menahan tombol ctrl/"
"command ketika mengeklik, dan seret mereka ke dalam kotak Istilah Model."

msgctxt "RegressionLinear|"
msgid "Include the intercept in the regression model."
msgstr "Sertakan intersep dalam model regresi."

msgctxt "RegressionLinear|"
msgid "Durbin-Watson statistic to test the autocorrelation of the residuals."
msgstr "Statistik Durbin-Watson untuk menguji korelasi otomatis dari residu."

msgctxt "RegressionLinear|"
msgid ""
"Unstandardized and standardized coefficient estimates, standard errors, t-"
"values, and their corresponding p-values."
msgstr ""
"Estimasi koefisien tidak terstandardisasi dan terstandardisasi, galat "
"standar, nilai-t, dan nilai-p mereka yang sesuai."

msgctxt "RegressionLinear|"
msgid ""
"Samples size, sample mean, sample standard deviation, and standard error of "
"the mean."
msgstr ""
"Ukuran sampel, rerata sampel, deviasi standar sampel, dan galat standar "
"rerata."

msgctxt "RegressionLinear|"
msgid "Semipartial and partial correlations."
msgstr "Korelasi semiparsial dan parsial."

msgctxt "RegressionLinear|"
msgid "Uses all complete observations for each individual pair of variables."
msgstr ""
"Menggunakan semua observasi lengkap untuk setiap pasangan individu variabel."

msgctxt "RegressionLinear|"
msgid ""
"Scatterplot of the values of the residuals against the dependent variable."
msgstr "Diagram pencaran dari nilai residu terhadap nilai dependen."

msgctxt "RegressionLinear|"
msgid ""
"Scatterplot of the values of the residuals against the predictor variables."
msgstr "Diagram pencaran dari nilai residu terhadap nilai prediktor."

msgctxt "RegressionLinear|"
msgid ""
"Scatterplot of the values of the residuals against the predicted values."
msgstr "Diagram pencaran dari nilai residu terhadap nilai terprediksi."

msgctxt "RegressionLinear|"
msgid "Use standardized residuals instead."
msgstr "Gunakan residu terstandarisasi sebagai pengganti."

msgctxt "RegressionLinearBayesian|"
msgid ""
"The Bayesian Linear Regression allows you to model a linear relationship "
"between one or more explanatory variable/s and a continuous dependent "
"variable.\n"
msgstr ""
"Regresi Logistik Bayes mengizinkan Anda untuk memodelkan hubungan linear "
"antara satu atau lebih variabel penjelasan dan variabel dependen "
"berkelanjutan.\n"

msgctxt "RegressionLinearBayesian|"
msgid "Assumptions"
msgstr "Asumsi"

msgctxt "RegressionLinearBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Continuous predictor variable(s). If ordinal variables are entered it is "
"assumed that their levels are equidistant. Hence, ordinal variables are "
"treated as continuous predictor variables."
msgstr ""
"Variabel prediktor kontinu. Jika variabel ordinal dimasukkan diasumsikan "
"bahwa tingkat mereka berjarak sama. Oleh karena itu, variabel ordinal "
"diperlakukan sebagai variabel prediktor kontinu."

msgctxt "RegressionLinearBayesian|"
msgid "The weights used for weighted least square regression."
msgstr "Berat digunakan untuk regresi kuadrat terlemah terberat."

msgctxt "RegressionLinearBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Displays plot of the most likely values of the effect size for each "
"predictor with their corresponding credible interval."
msgstr ""
"Menampilkan diagram nilai paling memungkinkan dari ukuran efek untuk setiap "
"prediktor dengan interval kredibel sesuai dengan mereka."

msgctxt "RegressionLinearBayesian|"
msgid "Displays the best model, meaning the most likely model given the data."
msgstr ""
"Menampilkan model terbaik, artinya model yang paling memungkinkan memberikan "
"data."

msgctxt "RegressionLinearBayesian|"
msgid ""
"By default, the output shows all the models computed. There is an option to "
"show the best n models."
msgstr ""
"Secara bawaan, luaran menampilkan semua model dihitung. Ada opsi untuk "
"menampilkan n model terbaik."

msgctxt "RegressionLinearBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Output table containing the mean, standard deviation, and sample size of the "
"variables selected."
msgstr ""
"Tabel luaran berisi rerata, deviasi standar, dan ukuran sampel dari variabel "
"dipilih."

msgctxt "RegressionLinearBayesian|"
msgid "All the independent variables that can be included in the model."
msgstr "Semua variabel independen yang dapat disertakan dalam model."

msgctxt "RegressionLinearBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Shows a histogram of the posterior inclusion probabilities. The dotted line "
"displays the prior inclusion probabilities."
msgstr ""
"Menampilkan histogram probabilitas inklusi posterior. Garis bertitik "
"menampilkan probabilitas inklusi priori."

msgctxt "RegressionLinearBayesian|"
msgid "Shows a heatmap of the log posterior odds against the model rank."
msgstr "Menampilkan heatmap ganjil posterior log terhadap peringkat model."

msgctxt "RegressionLinearBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Plots the residuals of the model averaged predictions against the residuals."
msgstr "Mendiagramkan residu dari prediksi dirata-rata model terhadap residu."

msgctxt "RegressionLinearBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Prior distribution for regression coefficients. Several options are "
"available:"
msgstr "Distribusi priori untuk koefisien regresi. Beberapa opsi tersedia:"

msgctxt "RegressionLinearBayesian|"
msgid "Compare models using the Bayesian Information Criterion."
msgstr "Bandingkan model menggunakan Kriteria Informasi Bayes."

msgctxt "RegressionLinearBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Global Empirical Bayes estimates of g in Zellner-Siow g-prior and model "
"probabilities. Uses an EM algorithm to find a common or global estimate of "
"g, averaged over all models. When it is not possible to enumerate all "
"models, the EM algorithm uses only the models sampled under EB-local."
msgstr ""
"Estimasi Bayes Empiris Global dari g di priori-g Zellner-Siow dan "
"probabilitas model. Menggunaakn algoritma EM untuk menemukan estimasi umum "
"atau global dari g, dirata-ratakan di atas semua model. Ketika itu tidak "
"memungkinkan untuk menghitung semua model, algoritma EM menggunakan hanya "
"model disampel di bawah lokal-EB."

msgctxt "RegressionLinearBayesian|"
msgid "Zellner's g-prior."
msgstr "Priori-g Zellner."

msgctxt "RegressionLinearBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Same as Hyper-g but uses a Laplace approximation to integrate over the prior "
"on g."
msgstr ""
"Sama seperti Hiper-g tetapi menggunakan perkiraan Laplace untuk "
"mengintegrasikan di atas priori pada g."

msgctxt "RegressionLinearBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Jeffreys-Zellner-Siow prior which uses the Jeffreys prior on sigma and the "
"Zellner-Siow Cauchy prior on the coefficients. The optional parameter can be "
"used to control the squared scale of the prior."
msgstr ""
"Priori Jeffreys-Zellner-Siow yang menggunakan priori Jeffreys pada sigma dan "
"priori Cauchy Zellner-Siow pada koefisien. Parameter opsional dapat "
"digunakan untuk mengontrol skala kuadrat priori."

msgctxt "RegressionLinearBayesian|"
msgid "Prior distribution on the models."
msgstr "Distribusi priori pada model."

msgctxt "RegressionLinearBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Default lambda = 1. Equivalent to a Beta binomial with a = 1 and b = lambda "
"* p, where p is the number of predictors in the model."
msgstr ""
"lambda bawaan = 1. Setara dengan binomial Beta dengan a = 1 dan b = lambda * "
"p, di mana p adalah jumlah prediktor dalam model."

msgctxt "RegressionLinearBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Default u = 1. Equivalent to a Beta binomial with a = 1 and b = p^u, where p "
"is the number of predictors in the model."
msgstr ""
"u bawaan = 1. Setara dengan binomial Beta dengan a = 1 dan b = p^u, di mana "
"p adalah jumlah prediktor dalam model."

msgctxt "RegressionLinearBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Indicates the sampling method to be used. It is recommended to use BAS when "
"the model space can be enumerated."
msgstr ""
"Mengindikasikan metode pensampelan yang digunakan. Itu direkomendasikan "
"untuk menggunakan BAS ketika ruang model dapat dihitung."

msgctxt "RegressionLinearBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Uses Bayesian Adaptive Sampling (without replacement). These can be updated "
"based on estimates of the marginal inclusion. No. models indicates the "
"number of models to sample without replacement. Setting the value to 0 "
"implies the analysis will attempt to enumerate all models."
msgstr ""
"Menggunakan Pensampelan Adaptif Bayes (tanpa pengganti). Ini dapat "
"diperbarui berdasarkan estimasi inklusi margin. Jml. model mengindikasikan "
"jumlah model untuk menyampelkan tanpa pengganti. Mengatur nilai ke 0 "
"menyiratkan analisis akan mencoba untuk menghitung semua model."

msgctxt "RegressionLinearBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Accuracy of credible intervals. There is an option to select the number of "
"samples used to estimate the credible interval. The more samples the more "
"accurate the credible intervals will be."
msgstr ""
"Akurasi interval kepercayaan. Ada opsi untuk memilih jumlah sampel digunakan "
"untuk mengestimasikan interval kepercayaan. Lebih banyak sampel lebih akurat "
"interval kredibel."

msgctxt "RegressionLogistic|"
msgid ""
"Logistic regression allows the user to model a linear relationship between "
"one or more explanatory variable/s and a categorical dependent variable.\n"
msgstr ""
"Regresi logistik mengizinkan pengguna untuk memodelkan hubungan linear "
"antara satu atau lebih variabel penjelasan dan variabel dependen "
"kategorikal.\n"

msgctxt "RegressionLogistic|"
msgid "Assumptions"
msgstr "Asumsi"

msgctxt "RegressionLogistic|"
msgid ""
"The variable of interest. This is also called the outcome variable. In case "
"of multiple dependent variables, specify the order in which the predictors "
"are entered into the model i.e., hierarchical regression analysis. A block "
"of one or more predictors represents one step in the hierarchy."
msgstr ""
"Variabel minat. Ini juga disebut variabel hasil. Jika beberapa variabel "
"dependen, tentukan urutan di mana prediktor dimasukkan ke dalam model yaitu, "
"analisis regresi hirarkikal. Blok dari satu atau lebih prediktor "
"merepresentasikan satu langkah di hirarki."

msgctxt "RegressionLogistic|"
msgid ""
"The independent variables and covariates included in the model. By default, "
"all the main effects and interaction effects of the specified independent "
"variables, and the covariates are included in the model."
msgstr ""
"Variabel independen dan kovariat disertakan dalam model. Secara bawaan, "
"semua efek utama dan efek interaksi dari variabel independen tertentu, dan "
"kovariat disertakan dalam model."

msgctxt "RegressionLogistic|"
msgid ""
"The levels of the dependent variable/s and the number of observations per "
"level."
msgstr "Tingkat dari variabel dependen dan jumlah observasi per tingkat."

msgctxt "RegressionLogistic|"
msgid ""
"The confusion matrix indicates how well the model predicts the outcomes. The "
"table is showing actual versus predicted outcomes and can be used to "
"determine the accuracy of the model."
msgstr ""
"Matriks kebingungan mengindikasikan seberapa model memprediksi hasil. Tabel "
"menampilkan hasil aktual vs terprediksi dan dapat digunakan untuk menentukan "
"akurasi model."

msgctxt "RegressionLogistic|"
msgid ""
"Coefficient estimates, standard errors, z-values, and their corresponding p-"
"values."
msgstr ""
"Estimasi koefisien, galat standar, nilai-z, dan nilai-p mereka yang sesuai."

msgctxt "RegressionLogistic|"
msgid ""
"By selecting this option, bootstrapped estimation is applied. By default, "
"the number of replications is set to 5000. This can be changed into the "
"desired number."
msgstr ""
"Dengan memilih opsi ini, estimasi terbootstrap diterapkan. Secara bawaan, "
"jumlah replikasi diatur ke 5000. Ini dapat diubah menjadi angka teringinkan."

msgctxt "RegressionLogistic|"
msgid ""
"Odds ratio is an indicator of the change in odds resulting from a unit "
"change in the predictor."
msgstr ""
"Rasio ganjil adalah indikator dari perubahan dalam ganjil menghasilkan dari "
"perubahan unit di prediktor."

msgctxt "RegressionLogistic|"
msgid "Area Under the Curve."
msgstr "Area di Bawah Kurva."

msgctxt "RegressionLogistic|"
msgid "Sensitivity describes the proportion of true positives."
msgstr "Sentivitas menjelaskan proporsi positif benar."

msgctxt "RegressionLogistic|"
msgid "Specificity describes the proportion of true negatives."
msgstr "Kespesifik menjelaskan proporsi negatif benar."

msgctxt "RegressionLogistic|"
msgid ""
"Precision describes the proportion of true positives to all positives. Also "
"called the positive predictive value."
msgstr ""
"Presisi menjelaskan proporsi positif benar ke semua positif. Juga disebut "
"nilai prediktif positif."

msgctxt "RegressionLogistic|"
msgid ""
"Another measure of the accuracy of predictions. Based on the mean squared "
"difference between predicted probabilities and the binary outcome. Lower "
"scores mean more accuracy."
msgstr ""
"Pengukuran lain dari akurasi prediksi. Berdasarkan perbedaan rerata kuadrat "
"antara probabilitas terprediksi dan hasil biner. Skor lebih rendah artinya "
"lebih akurat."

msgctxt "RegressionLogistic|"
msgid "A more theoretically robust and advanced alternative to the AUC."
msgstr "Alternatif AUC yang secara teoritis kuat dan lanjutan."

msgctxt "RegressionLogistic|"
msgid ""
"The plots are conditional in the sense that they display the probability of "
"the categorical dependent variable for all levels of the predictor variables "
"given the reference level of all other factors."
msgstr ""
"Diagram kondisional di artikan bahwa mereka menampilkan probabilitas "
"variabel dependen kategorikal untuk semua tingkat dari variabel prediktor "
"memberikan tingkat referensi dari semua faktor lain."

msgctxt "RegressionLogistic|"
msgid ""
"Scatterplot of the values of the residuals against the predicted values."
msgstr "Diagram pencaran dari nilai residu terhadap nilai terprediksi."

msgctxt "RegressionLogistic|"
msgid ""
"Scatterplot for every independent variable and covariate of the residuals "
"and the levels of the variable of interest."
msgstr ""
"Diagram pencaran untuk setiap variabel independen dan kovariat dari residu "
"dan tingkat dari variabel minat."

msgctxt "RegressionLogistic|"
msgid ""
"With the Squared Pearson residuals plot one can check for overdispersion of "
"the model. Overdispersion indicates that the actual data show greater "
"variability than the model has predicted."
msgstr ""
"Dengan Pearson Kuadrat diagram residu satu dapat memeriksa untuk atas "
"dispersi dari model. Atas dispersi mengindikasikan bahwa data aktual "
"menampilkan variabilitas lebih dari modeh telah diprediksi."

msgctxt "RegressionLogistic|"
msgid "Plots the model predictions against each independent variable."
msgstr "Mendiagramkan prediksi model terhadap setiap variabel independen."

msgctxt "RegressionLogistic|"
msgid "The standardized Pearson residuals."
msgstr "Residu Pearson terstandardisasi."

msgctxt "RegressionLogisticBayesian|"
msgid "Assumptions"
msgstr "Asumsi"

msgctxt "RegressionLogisticBayesian|"
msgid ""
"The variable of interest, also called outcome variable. Needs to be "
"categorical for this analysis."
msgstr ""
"Variabel minat, juga disebut variabel hasil. Harus berupa kategorikal untuk "
"analisis ini."

msgctxt "RegressionLogisticBayesian|"
msgid ""
"The variables that are manipulated/define the different groups. These are "
"also called the independent variables."
msgstr ""
"Variabel yang dimanipulasi/tentukan grup berbeda. Ini juga disebut variabel "
"independen."

msgctxt "RegressionLogisticBayesian|"
msgid "Displays the best model, meaning the most likely model given the data."
msgstr ""
"Menampilkan model terbaik, artinya model yang paling memungkinkan memberikan "
"data."

msgctxt "RegressionLogisticBayesian|"
msgid ""
"By default, the output shows all the models computed. There is an option to "
"show the best n models."
msgstr ""
"Secara bawaan, luaran menampilkan semua model dihitung. Ada opsi untuk "
"menampilkan n model terbaik."

msgctxt "RegressionLogisticBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Output table containing the mean, standard deviation, and sample size of the "
"variables selected."
msgstr ""
"Tabel luaran berisi rerata, deviasi standar, dan ukuran sampel dari variabel "
"dipilih."

msgctxt "RegressionLogisticBayesian|"
msgid "All the independent variables that can be included in the model."
msgstr "Semua variabel independen yang dapat disertakan dalam model."

msgctxt "RegressionLogisticBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Shows a histogram of the posterior inclusion probabilities. The dotted line "
"displays the prior inclusion probabilities."
msgstr ""
"Menampilkan histogram probabilitas inklusi posterior. Garis bertitik "
"menampilkan probabilitas inklusi priori."

msgctxt "RegressionLogisticBayesian|"
msgid "Shows a heatmap of the log posterior odds against the model rank."
msgstr "Menampilkan heatmap ganjil posterior log terhadap peringkat model."

msgctxt "RegressionLogisticBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Plots the residuals of the model averaged predictions against the residuals."
msgstr "Mendiagramkan residu dari prediksi dirata-rata model terhadap residu."

msgctxt "RegressionLogisticBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Prior distribution for regression coefficients. Several options are "
"available:"
msgstr "Distribusi priori untuk koefisien regresi. Beberapa opsi tersedia:"

msgctxt "RegressionLogisticBayesian|"
msgid "Compare models using the Bayesian Information Criterion."
msgstr "Bandingkan model menggunakan Kriteria Informasi Bayes."

msgctxt "RegressionLogisticBayesian|"
msgid "Prior distribution on the models."
msgstr "Distribusi priori pada model."

msgctxt "RegressionLogisticBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Default lambda = 1. Equivalent to a Beta binomial with a = 1 and b = lambda "
"* p, where p is the number of predictors in the model."
msgstr ""
"lambda bawaan = 1. Setara dengan binomial Beta dengan a = 1 dan b = lambda * "
"p, di mana p adalah jumlah prediktor dalam model."

msgctxt "RegressionLogisticBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Default u = 1. Equivalent to a Beta binomial with a = 1 and b = p^u, where p "
"is the number of predictors in the model."
msgstr ""
"u bawaan = 1. Setara dengan binomial Beta dengan a = 1 dan b = p^u, di mana "
"p adalah jumlah prediktor dalam model."

msgctxt "RegressionLogisticBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Indicates the sampling method to be used. It is recommended to use BAS when "
"the model space can be enumerated."
msgstr ""
"Mengindikasikan metode pensampelan yang digunakan. Itu direkomendasikan "
"untuk menggunakan BAS ketika ruang model dapat dihitung."

msgctxt "RegressionLogisticBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Uses Bayesian Adaptive Sampling (without replacement). These can be updated "
"based on estimates of the marginal inclusion. No. models indicates the "
"number of models to sample without replacement. Setting the value to 0 "
"implies the analysis will attempt to enumerate all models."
msgstr ""
"Menggunakan Pensampelan Adaptif Bayes (tanpa pengganti). Ini dapat "
"diperbarui berdasarkan estimasi inklusi margin. Jml. model mengindikasikan "
"jumlah model untuk menyampelkan tanpa pengganti. Mengatur nilai ke 0 "
"menyiratkan analisis akan mencoba untuk menghitung semua model."

msgctxt "RegressionLogisticBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Accuracy of credible intervals. There is an option to select the number of "
"samples used to estimate the credible interval. The more samples the more "
"accurate the credible intervals will be."
msgstr ""
"Akurasi interval kepercayaan. Ada opsi untuk memilih jumlah sampel digunakan "
"untuk mengestimasikan interval kepercayaan. Lebih banyak sampel lebih akurat "
"interval kredibel."

msgctxt "EmmComponent|"
msgid ""
"Width/level of the confidence interval for the estimated marginal means."
msgstr "Lebar/tingkat interval kepercayaan untuk rerata margin terestimasi."

msgctxt "EmmComponent|"
msgid ""
"Value to which the estimated marginal means will be compared to. The default "
"value is set to 0 and can be changed by the user."
msgstr ""
"Nilai mana rerata margin terestimasi akan dibandingkan. Nilai bawaannya "
"diatur ke 0 dan dapat diubah oleh pengguna."

msgctxt "EmmComponent|"
msgid ""
"Decide whether the estimated marginal means should be computed on the "
"response scale or the untransformed linear scale. The former is selected by "
"default."
msgstr ""
"Putuskan apakah rerata margin terestimasi harus dihitung pada skala "
"tanggapan atau skala linear tidak bertransformasi. Former dipilih secara "
"bawaan."

msgctxt "EmmComponent|"
msgid ""
"Create a table for specifying contrasts based on the estimated marginal "
"means. The row indices correspond to the 'Level' column in the estimated "
"marginal means output table. Columns with variable names contain the "
"(combinations of) variable levels for each estimated marginal mean. Columns "
"named Contrast 1, 2, ... are used for specifying the contrasts. To set a "
"contrast between two marginal means, enter -1 and 1 to the corresponding "
"rows. Interactions can be tested by specifying differences between the "
"changes in marginal means of one variable across levels of another variable."
msgstr ""
"Buat tabel untuk menspesifikasikan kontras berdasarkan rerata margin "
"terestimasi. Indeks baris sesuai dengan kolom 'Tingkat’ di tabel luaran "
"rerata margin terestimasi. Kolom dengan nama variabel berisi (kombinasi "
"dari) tingkat variabel untuk setiap rerata margin terestimasi. Kolom bernama "
"Kontras 1, 2, ... digunakan untuk menspesifikasikan kontras. Untuk mengatur "
"kontras antara dua rerata margin, masukkan -1 dan 1 ke baris yang sesuai. "
"Interaksi dapat diuji dengan menspesifikasikan perbedaan antara perubahan di "
"rerata margin dari satu variabel di seluruh tingkat variabel lain."

msgctxt "ExportBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Appends the posterior mean of the residuals as a new column in the data file."
msgstr ""
"Menambahkan rerata posterior dari residu sebagai kolom baru di berkas data."

msgctxt "ExportBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Appends the posterior standard deviation of the residuals as a new column in "
"the data file."
msgstr ""
"Menambahkan deviasi standar posterior dari residu sebagai kolom baru di "
"berkas data."

msgctxt "GlmInputComponent|"
msgid "The response variable."
msgstr "Variabel tanggapan."

msgctxt "GlmInputComponent|"
msgid "Quantitative variables, such as age, height and IQ."
msgstr "Variabel kuantitatif, seperti usia, tinggi dan IQ."

msgctxt "GlmInputComponent|"
msgid "Distribution of the response variable:"
msgstr "Distribusi variabel tanggapan:"

msgctxt "GlmResidualAnalysisPlotsComponent|"
msgid ""
"Provides different types of diagnostic plots based on deviance residuals."
msgstr ""
"Menyediakan jenis diagram diagnostik berbeda berdasarkan residu devians."

msgctxt "GlmResidualAnalysisPlotsComponent|"
msgid ""
"Displays a scatter plot of the standardized deviance residuals against the "
"fitted values (with constant-information scale transformations)."
msgstr ""
"Menampilkan diagram pencaran dari residu devians terstandardisasi terhadap "
"nilai disesuai (dengan transformasi skala informasi-konstan)."

msgctxt "GlmResidualAnalysisPlotsComponent|"
msgid ""
"Displays a scatter plot of the standardized deviance residuals against every "
"predictor on its original scale."
msgstr ""
"Menampilkan diagram pencaran dari residu devians terstandardisasi terhadap "
"setiap prediktor pada skala aslinya."

msgctxt "GlmResidualAnalysisPlotsComponent|"
msgid "Displays a Q-Q plot of the standardized deviance residuals."
msgstr "Menampilkan diagram Q-Q dari residu devians terstandardisasi."

msgctxt "GlmResidualAnalysisPlotsComponent|"
msgid ""
"Provides different types of diagnostic plots based on Pearson residuals."
msgstr ""
"Menyediakan jenis diagram diagnostik berbeda berdasarkan residu Pearson."

msgctxt "GlmResidualAnalysisPlotsComponent|"
msgid ""
"Displays a scatter plot of the standardized Pearson residuals against the "
"fitted values (with constant-information scale transformations)."
msgstr ""
"Menampilkan diagram pencaran dari residu Pearson terstandardisasi terhadap "
"nilai disesuai (dengan transformasi skala informasi-konstan)."

msgctxt "GlmResidualAnalysisPlotsComponent|"
msgid ""
"Displays a scatter plot of the standardized Pearson residuals against every "
"predictor on its original scale."
msgstr ""
"Menampilkan diagram pencaran dari residu Pearson terstandardisasi terhadap "
"setiap prediktor pada skala aslinya."

msgctxt "GlmResidualAnalysisPlotsComponent|"
msgid "Displays a Q-Q plot of the standardized Pearson residuals."
msgstr "Menampilkan diagram Q-Q dari residu Pearson terstandardisasi."

msgctxt "GlmResidualAnalysisPlotsComponent|"
msgid ""
"Provides different types of diagnostic plots based on quantile residuals. "
"Highly recommended for discrete families (e.g., Bernoulli, Binomial, "
"Poisson)."
msgstr ""
"Menyediakan jenis diagram diagnostik berbeda berdasarkan residu kuantil. "
"Sangat direkomendasikan untuk keluarga diskrit (mis., Bernoulli, Binomial, "
"Poisson)."

msgctxt "GlmResidualAnalysisPlotsComponent|"
msgid ""
"Displays a scatter plot of the standardized quantile residuals against the "
"fitted values (with constant-information scale transformations)."
msgstr ""
"Menampilkan diagram pencaran dari residu kuantil terstandardisasi terhadap "
"nilai disesuai (dengan transformasi skala informasi-konstan)."

msgctxt "GlmResidualAnalysisPlotsComponent|"
msgid ""
"Displays a scatter plot of the standardized quantile residuals against every "
"predictor on its original scale."
msgstr ""
"Menampilkan diagram pencaran dari residu kuantil terstandardisasi terhadap "
"setiap prediktor pada skala aslinya."

msgctxt "GlmResidualAnalysisPlotsComponent|"
msgid "Displays a Q-Q plot of the standardized quantile residuals."
msgstr "Menampilkan diagram Q-Q dari residu kuantil terstandardisasi."

msgctxt "GlmResidualAnalysisPlotsComponent|"
msgid "Displays partial residual plots across predictors."
msgstr "Menampilkan diagram residu sebagian di seluruh prediktor."

msgctxt "GlmResidualAnalysisPlotsComponent|"
msgid ""
"Displays a scatter plot of the model's working responses z against the "
"predicted linear predictor values."
msgstr ""
"Menampilkan diagram pencaran dari tanggapan pekerjaan model z terhadap nilai "
"prediktor linear terprediksi."

msgctxt "OutlierComponent|"
msgid "Displays descriptive statistics of the residuals and predicted values."
msgstr "Menampilkan statistik deskriptif dari residu dan nilai terprediksi."

msgctxt "OutlierComponent|"
msgid ""
"Provides casewise diagnostics for residuals, displaying cases above a "
"threshold based on standardized residuals (default: 3) or Cook's distance "
"(default: 1), or displaying all cases."
msgstr ""
"Menyediakan diagnostik kasus untuk residu, menampilkan kasus di atas ambang "
"batas berdasarkan residu terstandardisasi (bawaan: 3) atau jarak Cook "
"(bawaan: 1), atau menampilkan semua kasus."

msgctxt "OutlierComponent|"
msgid ""
"The difference between a parameter estimated using all cases and estimated "
"when one case is excluded. Indicated in the table when the absolute value of "
"DFBETAS is greater than 1."
msgstr ""
"Perbedaan antara parameter diestimasikan menggunakan semua kasus dan "
"diestimasikan ketika satu kasus dikecualikan. Diindikasikan di tabel ketika "
"nilai absolut DFBETAS lebih dari 1."

msgctxt "OutlierComponent|"
msgid ""
"The difference between the predicted value for a case when the model is "
"estimated including or excluding that case. Indicated in the table when the "
"absolute value of DFFITS is greater than 3 * sqrt(k/(n-k))."
msgstr ""
"Perbedaan antara nilai terprediksi untuk kasus ketika model diestimasikan "
"menyertakan atau mengecualikan kasus itu. Diindikasikan di tabel ketika "
"nilai absolut DFFITS lebih dari 3 * sqrt(k/(n-k))."

msgctxt "OutlierComponent|"
msgid ""
"The degree to which a case influences the variance of the regression "
"parameters. Indicated in the table when the covariance ratio is greater than "
"3 * k/(n-k)."
msgstr ""
"Derajat mana kasus memengaruhi varians parameter regresi. Diindikasikan di "
"tabel ketika rasio kovarians lebih dari 3 * k/(n-k)."

msgctxt "OutlierComponent|"
msgid ""
"The influence of the observed value of the outcome variable over the "
"predicted values. Indicated in the table when the leverage is greater than 3 "
"* k/n."
msgstr ""
"Influens nilai terobservasi dari variabel hasil di atas nilai terprediksi. "
"Diindikasikan di tabel ketika tingkatan lebih dari 3 * k/n."

msgctxt "OutlierComponent|"
msgid ""
"Measures the distance of cases from the mean(s) of the predictor variable(s)."
msgstr "Mengukur jarak kasus dari rerata dari variabel prediktor."

msgctxt "Correlation|"
msgid "Assumptions (Spearman's rho and Kendall's tau)."
msgstr "Asumsi (rho Spearman dan tau Kendall)."

msgctxt "Correlation|"
msgid "Variables for which to compute the correlation coefficient."
msgstr "Variabel yang mana untuk menghitung koefisien korelasi."

msgctxt "Correlation|"
msgid "Pearson's product moment correlation coefficient."
msgstr "Koefisien korelasi momen produk Pearson."

msgctxt "Correlation|"
msgid ""
"Spearman's rank-order correlation coefficient to quantify the monotonic "
"association between two variables by ranking the observations. Use when the "
"data are not normally distributed."
msgstr ""
"Koefisien korelasi urutan peringkat Spearman untuk menghitung asosiasi "
"monoton antara dua variabel dengan memeringkatkan observasi. Gunakan ketika "
"data tidak secara normal didistribusikan."

msgctxt "Correlation|"
msgid ""
"Kendall's tau-b rank-order correlation coefficient to quantify the monotonic "
"association between two variables by comparing concordant and non-concordant "
"pairs. Use when the data are not normally distributed."
msgstr ""
"Koefisien korelasi urutan peringkat b-tau Kendall untuk menghitung asosiasi "
"monoton antara dua variabel dengan membandingkan pasangan konkordan dan non-"
"konkordan. Gunakan ketika data tidak secara normal didistribusikan."

msgctxt "Correlation|"
msgid ""
"Displays a table where one row corresponds to one pair of the specified "
"variables, and the scatter plots are shown individually for each pair. If "
"unticked, the results are presented in matrix format, with variable names in "
"the columns and rows."
msgstr ""
"Menampilkan tabel di mana satu baris menyesuaikan dengan satu pasangan dari "
"variabel tertentu, dan diagram pencaran ditampilkan secara individu untuk "
"setiap pasangan. Jika tidak dicentang, hasil dipresentasikan dalam format "
"matriks, dengan nama variabel di kolom dan baris."

msgctxt "Correlation|"
msgid "Displays the p-value corresponding to the observed correlation."
msgstr "Menampilkan nilai-p sesuai dengan korelasi terobservasi."

msgctxt "Correlation|"
msgid "Marks statistically significant correlations."
msgstr "Menandai secara statistik korelasi signifikan."

msgctxt "Correlation|"
msgid ""
"Confidence intervals for the population correlation (available only for the "
"Pearson correlation). The default is set at 95%, but this percentage can be "
"adjusted. Additionally, you can set up bootstrap estimation, using 1000 "
"replications by default but it can be modified to your desired number."
msgstr ""
"Interval kepercayaan untuk korelasi populasi (tersedia hanya untuk korelasi "
"Pearson). Bawaannya diatur ke 95%, tetapi persentase ini dapat disesuaikan. "
"Secara tambahan, Anda dapat mengatur estimasi bootstrap, menggunakan 1000 "
"replikasi secara bawaan tetapi itu dapat dimodifikasikan ke angka Anda yang "
"diinginkan."

msgctxt "Correlation|"
msgid ""
"Shows the maximum ratio of the likelihood of the obtained p value under H1 "
"vs the likelihood of the obtained p value under H0. For example, if the two-"
"sided p-value equals .05, the Vovk-Sellke MPR equals 2.46, indicating that "
"this p-value is at most 2.46 times more likely to occur under H1 than under "
"H0."
msgstr ""
"Menampilkan rasio maksimum dari kemungkinan nilai p terambil di bawah H1 vs "
"nilai p terambil di bawah H0. Contohnya, jika nilai-p dua sisi sama "
"dengan .05, MPR Vovk-Sellke sama dengan 2.46, mengindikasikan bahwa nilai-p "
"ini kemungkinan lebih banyak 2.46 kali lebih besar terjadi di bawah H1 dari "
"di bawah H0."

msgctxt "Correlation|"
msgid "The covariance between each pair of variables."
msgstr "Kovarians antara setiap pasangan variabel."

msgctxt "Correlation|"
msgid ""
"One-sided alternative hypothesis that the population correlation is less "
"than 0."
msgstr "Hipotesis alternatif satu sisi bahwa korelasi populasi kurang dari 0."

msgctxt "Correlation|"
msgid ""
"Displays the specified confidence interval around the regression line on the "
"plot."
msgstr ""
"Menampilkan interval kepercayaan dispesifikasikan dikelilingi garis regresi "
"pada diagram."

msgctxt "Correlation|"
msgid ""
"Displays a correlation heatmap for Pearson, Spearman, and Kendall's tau B "
"coefficients separately."
msgstr ""
"Menampilkan heatmap korelasi untuk koefisien B tau Pearsn, Spearman, dan "
"Kendall secara terpisah."

msgctxt "Correlation|"
msgid "Means and standard deviations."
msgstr "Mean dan deviasi standar."

msgctxt "Correlation|"
msgid "Cross-product deviations and covariances."
msgstr "Deviasi dan kovarians lintas produk."

msgctxt "Correlation|"
msgid "Uses only complete cases across all variables."
msgstr "Menggunakan hanya kasus lengkap melintasi semua variabel."

msgctxt "CorrelationBayesian|"
msgid ""
"The Bayesian Correlation analysis allows for the estimation of the "
"population correlation, as well as the comparison of hypotheses. The three "
"comparisons are (i) between the null hypothesis (H0) that the correlation "
"between pairs of variables equals 0, and the alternative hypothesis (H1) "
"that the population correlation takes its value between -1 and 1; (ii) "
"between H0 and the alternative hypothesis (H+) that the population "
"correlation is positive; and (iii) between H0 and the alternative hypothesis "
"(H-) that the population correlation is negative. All possible pairs of the "
"specified variables are analyzed.\n"
msgstr ""
"Analisis Korelasi Bayes mengizinkan untuk estimasi korelasi populasi, dan "
"perbandingan hipotesis juga. Tiga perbandingan adalah (i) antara hipotesis "
"null (H0) bahwa korelasi antara pasangan variabel sama dengan 0, dan "
"hipotesis alternatif (H1) bahwa korelasi populasi mengambil nilainya antara "
"-1 dan 1; (ii) antara H0 dan hipotesis alternatif (H+) bahwa korelasi "
"populasi adalah positif; dan (iii) antara H0 dan hipotesis alternatif (H-) "
"bahwa korelasi populasi adalah negatif. Semua pasangan variabel tertentu "
"yang memungkinkan dianalisis.\n"

msgctxt "CorrelationBayesian|"
msgid "Variables for which to compute the correlation coefficient."
msgstr "Variabel yang mana untuk menghitung koefisien korelasi."

msgctxt "CorrelationBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Pearson's product moment correlation coefficient. This is the famous r value."
msgstr "Koefisien korelasi momen produk Pearson. Ini adalah nilai r terkenal."

msgctxt "CorrelationBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Kendall's tau-b rank-order correlation coefficient to quantify the monotonic "
"association between two variables by comparing concordant and non-concordant "
"pairs. Use when the data are not normally distributed."
msgstr ""
"Koefisien korelasi urutan peringkat b-tau Kendall untuk menghitung asosiasi "
"monoton antara dua variabel dengan membandingkan pasangan konkordan dan non-"
"konkordan. Gunakan ketika data tidak secara normal didistribusikan."

msgctxt "CorrelationBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Displays a table where one row corresponds to one pair of the specified "
"variables. If unticked, the results are presented in matrix format, with "
"variable names in the columns and rows."
msgstr ""
"Menampilkan tabel di mana satu baris menyesuaikan dengan satu pasangan dari "
"variabel dispesifikasikan. Jika tidak dicentang, hasil dipresentasikan dalam "
"format matriks, dengan nama variabel di kolom dan baris."

msgctxt "CorrelationBayesian|"
msgid "Reports Bayes factor for each test."
msgstr "Melaporkan faktor Bayes untuk setiap uji."

msgctxt "CorrelationBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Indicates which correlation coefficients yield Bayes factors greater than "
"10, 30, and 100."
msgstr ""
"Mengindikasikan mana koefisien korelasi menghasilkan faktor Bayes lebih dari "
"10, 30, dan 100."

msgctxt "CorrelationBayesian|"
msgid "Reports the sample size for each test."
msgstr "Melaporkan ukuran sampel untuk setiap uji."

msgctxt "CorrelationBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Displays central 95% credible intervals for the correlation coefficient. The "
"percentage can be changed."
msgstr ""
"Menampilkan pusat 95% interval kredibel untuk koefisien korelasi. Persentase "
"dapat diubah."

msgctxt "CorrelationBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Displays a grid of scatterplots for each possible combination of the "
"selected variables. These are placed above the diagonal."
msgstr ""
"Menampilkan kisi diagram bercak untuk setiap kombinasi memungkinkan dari "
"variabel terpilih. Ini ditempatkan di atas diagonal."

msgctxt "CorrelationBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Displays a histogram and the corresponding density plot for each variable. "
"These are placed on the diagonal."
msgstr ""
"Menampilkan histogram dan diagram kepadatan sesuai untuk setiap variabel. "
"Ini ditempatkan pada diagonal."

msgctxt "CorrelationBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Displays posterior distribution of the correlation coefficient for each "
"possible combination of the selected variables. These are placed below the "
"diagonal."
msgstr ""
"Menampilkan distribusi posterior dari koefisien korelasi untuk setiap "
"kombinasi memungkinkan dari variabel terpilih. Ini ditempatkan di bawah "
"diagonal."

msgctxt "CorrelationBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Stretched beta prior width: Width of the scaled beta distribution on the "
"correlation under the alternative hypothesis; default is 1. The lower this "
"value, the more concentrated the prior density is around 0. Value must be "
"between 0 and 2."
msgstr ""
"Lebar priori beta diperluas: Lebar dari distribusi beta berskala pada "
"korelasi di bawah hipotesis alternatif; bawaannya adalah 1. Lebih rendah "
"nilai ini, lebih berkonsentrasi kepadatan priori di antara 0. Nilai harus "
"antara 0 dan 2."

msgctxt "GeneralizedLinearModel|"
msgid "Selected by default. This adds an intercept term to the model."
msgstr "Dipilih secara bawaan. Ini menambahkan istilah intersep ke model."

msgctxt "GeneralizedLinearModel|"
msgid ""
"Selected by default. This gives a table summarizing the model's parameter "
"estimates, standard error around the parameter estimates, the test statistic "
"(t or z), and the p-value."
msgstr ""
"Dipilih secara bawaan. Ini memberikan tabel meringkaskan estimasi parameter "
"model, galat standar di antara estimasi parameter, statistik uji (t atau z), "
"dan nilai-p."

msgctxt "GeneralizedLinearModel|"
msgid ""
"A table showing the top n cases, ranked descendingly based on the size of "
"the residuals. Note that the shown cases are not necessarily outliers. The "
"column Case Number refers to the row number of the observation in the data "
"set."
msgstr ""
"Tabel menampilkan kasus n atas, diperingkatkan secara menurun berdasarkan "
"ukuran residu. Dicatat bahwa kasus ditampilkan tidak perlu outlier. Kolom "
"Angka Kasus berkaitan dengan jumlah baris observasi di rangkaian data."

msgctxt "GeneralizedLinearModel|"
msgid "Top n standardized quantile residuals."
msgstr "Residu kuantil terstandardisasi n teratas."

msgctxt "GeneralizedLinearModel|"
msgid "Top n standardized deviance residuals."
msgstr "Residu devians terstandardisasi n teratas."

msgctxt "GeneralizedLinearModel|"
msgid "Top n studentized deviance residuals."
msgstr "Residu devians terstudent n teratas."

msgctxt "GeneralizedLinearModel|"
msgid ""
"Indicates how much of a predictor’s variance is not explained by other "
"predictors."
msgstr ""
"Mengindikasikan seberapa varians prediktor tidak dijelaskan oleh prediktor "
"lain."

msgctxt "GeneralizedLinearModel|"
msgid ""
"Variance inflation factor, which indicates how much variance of a predictor "
"is inflated by multicollinearity among the predictor variables."
msgstr ""
"Faktor inflasi varians, yang mana mengindikasikan seberapa varians prediktor "
"diinflasikan oleh multikolinearitas di antara variabel prediktor."

msgctxt "RegressionLinear|"
msgid ""
"All predictors are entered simultaneously, and then removed sequentially "
"based on the criterion specified in Stepping method criteria."
msgstr ""
"Semua prediktor dimasukkan sekaligus, dan kemudia dihapus secara sekuensial "
"berdasarkan kriteria dispesifikasikan di kriteria metode Langkah."

msgctxt "RegressionLinear|"
msgid ""
"Categorical predictor variable(s). Ordinal variables here are treated as "
"categorical predictor variables, thus, the ordinal information is ignored."
msgstr ""
"Variabel prediktor kategorikal. Variabel ordinal di sini diperlakukan "
"sebagai nilai prediktor kategorikal, sehingga, informasi ordinal diabaikan."

msgctxt "RegressionLinear|"
msgid "The weights used for weighted least squares regression."
msgstr "Berat digunakan untuk regresi kuadrat terlemah terberat."

msgctxt "RegressionLinear|"
msgid "Components and model terms."
msgstr "Istilah komponen dan model."

msgctxt "RegressionLinear|"
msgid ""
"Change in R squared between the different models, with corresponding "
"significance test."
msgstr ""
"Perubahan di R kuadrat antara model berbeda, dengan menyesuaikan uji "
"signifikan."

msgctxt "RegressionLinear|"
msgid ""
"Change in F-statistic between the different models, with corresponding "
"significance test."
msgstr ""
"Perubahan di statistik-F antara model berbeda, dengan menyesuaikan uji "
"signifikan."

msgctxt "RegressionLinear|"
msgid ""
"Displays Akaike Information Criterion and Bayesian Information Criterion."
msgstr "Menampilkan Kriteria Informasi Akaike dan Kriteria Informasi Bayes."

msgctxt "RegressionLinear|"
msgid ""
"Apply bootstrapped estimation. By default, the number of replications is set "
"to 1000, but this can be changed to the desired number."
msgstr ""
"Terapkan estimasi ter-bootstrap. Secara bawaan, jumlah replikasi diatur ke "
"1000, tetapi ini dapat diubah ke angka yang diinginkan."

msgctxt "RegressionLinear|"
msgid ""
"Includes confidence intervals for the estimated mean difference. By default "
"the confidence level is set to 95%, but this can be changed to the desired "
"percentage."
msgstr ""
"Menyertakan interval kepercayaan untuk perbedaan rerata terestimasi. Secara "
"bawaan tingkat kepercayaan diatur ke 95%, tetapi ini dapat diubah ke "
"persentase yang diinginkan."

msgctxt "RegressionLinear|"
msgid ""
"Displays Tolerance and Variance Inflation Factor for each predictor in the "
"model in order to assess multicollinearity."
msgstr ""
"Menampilkan Faktor Inflasi Toleransi dan Varians untuk setiap prediktor di "
"model untuk mengevaluasi multikolinearitas."

msgctxt "RegressionLinear|"
msgid ""
"Shows the maximum ratio of the likelihood of the obtained p-value under H1 "
"vs the likelihood of the obtained p value under H0. For example, if the two-"
"sided p-value equals .05, the Vovk-Sellke MPR equals 2.46, indicating that "
"this p-value is at most 2.46 times more likely to occur under H1 than under "
"H0."
msgstr ""
"Menampilkan rasio maksimum dari kemungkinan nilai-p terambil di bawah H1 vs "
"kemungkinan nilai p terambil di bawah H0. Contohnya, jika nilai-p dua arah "
"sama dengan .05, MPR Vovk-Sellke sama dengan 2.46, mengindikasikan bahwa "
"nilai-p ini kemungkinan lebih banyak 2.46 kali lebih besar terjadi di bawah "
"H1 dari di bawah H0."

msgctxt "RegressionLinear|"
msgid ""
"Separate ANOVA table for each model, i.e., each step in Backward, Forward, "
"and Stepwise regression."
msgstr ""
"Pisahkan tabel ANOVA untuk setiap model, yaitu, setiap langkah di regresi "
"Mundur, Maju, dan Langkah."

msgctxt "RegressionLinear|"
msgid "Displays the covariance matrix of the predictor variables, per model."
msgstr "Menampilkan matriks kovarians dari variabel prediktor, per model."

msgctxt "RegressionLinear|"
msgid ""
"Collinearity statistics, eigenvalues, condition indices, and variance "
"proportions."
msgstr ""
"Statistik kolinearitas, nilai eigen, indeks kondisi, dan proporsi varians."

msgctxt "RegressionLinear|"
msgid ""
"Use p-value as criterion for adding and removing predictors in Backward, "
"Forward, and Stepwise regression."
msgstr ""
"Gunakan nilai-p sebagai kriteria untuk menambahkan dan menghapus prediktor "
"di regresi Mundur, Maju, dan Langkah."

msgctxt "RegressionLinear|"
msgid ""
"Adds predictor if the p-value of the regression coefficient < x; default is "
"x=0.05."
msgstr ""
"Menghapus prediktor jika nilai-p dari koefisien regresi adalah < x; "
"bawaannya adalah x=0.05."

msgctxt "RegressionLinear|"
msgid ""
"Removes predictor if the p-value of the regression coefficient > x; default "
"is x=0.1."
msgstr ""
"Menghapus prediktor jika nilai-p dari koefisien regresi adalah < x; "
"bawaannya adalah x=0.1."

msgctxt "RegressionLinear|"
msgid "Use F-value as criterion for adding and removing predictors."
msgstr ""
"Gunakan nilai-F sebagai kriteria untuk menambahkan dan menghapus prediktor."

msgctxt "RegressionLinear|"
msgid ""
"Adds predictor if the F-value (t^2) of the regression coefficient is > x; "
"default is x=3.84."
msgstr ""
"Menambahkan prediktor jika nilai-F (t^2) dari koefisien regresi adalah > x; "
"bawaannya adalah x=3.84."

msgctxt "RegressionLinear|"
msgid ""
"Removes predictor if the F-value (t^2) of the regression coefficient is < x; "
"default is x=2.71."
msgstr ""
"Menghapus prediktor jika nilai-F (t^2) dari koefisien regresi adalah < x; "
"bawaannya adalah x=2.71."

msgctxt "RegressionLinear|"
msgid "Uses only complete cases across all variables."
msgstr "Menggunakan hanya kasus lengkap melintasi semua variabel."

msgctxt "RegressionLinear|"
msgid ""
"If the assumptions of the linear regression model are tenable, then these "
"residuals should scatter randomly about a horizontal line. Any systematic "
"pattern or clustering of the residuals suggests model assumption violations."
msgstr ""
"Jika asumsi model regresi linear dapat disewa, kemudian residu ini harus "
"bercak secara acak tentang garis horizontal. Pola atau klaster sistematis "
"residu apa pun menyarankan pelanggaran asumsi model."

msgctxt "RegressionLinear|"
msgid "Displays a histogram of residual values."
msgstr "Menampilkan histogram nilai residu."

msgctxt "RegressionLinear|"
msgid ""
"These plots are scatterplots of the residuals from two regressions - "
"regressing the dependent variable on all other predictors, and regressing a "
"particular predictor (i.e., as dependent variable) on all other predictors-"
"then plotting the residuals against each other."
msgstr ""
"Diagram ini diagram pencaran residu dari dua regresi - meregresi variabel "
"dependen pada semua prediktor lain, dan meregresi prediktor sebagian (yaitu, "
"sebagai variabel dependen) pada semua prediktor lain-kemudian mendiagramkan "
"residu terhadap yang lain."

msgctxt "RegressionLinear|"
msgid ""
"Displays the specified confidence interval around the regression line on the "
"plot."
msgstr ""
"Menampilkan interval kepercayaan dispesifikasikan dikelilingi garis regresi "
"pada diagram."

msgctxt "RegressionLinear|"
msgid ""
"Visualization of how a change in a predictor affects the predicted outcome, "
"holding other variables constant."
msgstr ""
"Visualisasi bagaimana perubahan di prediktor berdampak hasil terprediksi, "
"menahan batasan variabel lain."

msgctxt "RegressionLinearBayesian|"
msgid "Drag the relevant dependent variable(s) to this box."
msgstr "Sertekan variabel dependen relevan ke kotak ini."

msgctxt "RegressionLinearBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Output table containing the Marginal Posterior Summaries of Coefficients."
msgstr "Tabel luaran berisi Ringkasan Posterior Margin Koefisien."

msgctxt "RegressionLinearBayesian|"
msgid "Compares across all models."
msgstr "Membandingkan di seluruh model."

msgctxt "RegressionLinearBayesian|"
msgid "Compares across matched models."
msgstr "Membandingkan di seluruh model cocok."

msgctxt "RegressionLinearBayesian|"
msgid "Omits the intercept in the plot display."
msgstr "Menghilangkan intersep di tampilan diagram."

msgctxt "RegressionLinearBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Displays the most complex model, meaning the model which includes all the "
"predictors."
msgstr ""
"Menampilkan model paling kompleks, artinya model mana menyertakan semua "
"prediktor."

msgctxt "RegressionLinearBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Displays the median model, meaning the smallest model in which all the "
"predictors are more likely to be part of the true model than not given the "
"data. i.e., has a posterior inclusion probability equal or greater than 0.5."
msgstr ""
"Menampilkan model media, artinya model terkecil di mana semua prediktor "
"lebih memungkinkan bagian dari model benar daripada tidak ada data "
"diberikan. Yaitu, memiliki probabilitas inklusi posterior sama atau lebih "
"dari 0.5."

msgctxt "RegressionLinearBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Displays the model in which the predictor coefficients are averaged out "
"across all models."
msgstr ""
"Menampilkan model di mana koefisien prediktor direratakan di seluruh model."

msgctxt "RegressionLinearBayesian|"
msgid "Compares each model against the model selected here."
msgstr "Membandingkan setiap model melawan model dipilih di sini."

msgctxt "RegressionLinearBayesian|"
msgid "All models are compared to the best model."
msgstr "Semua model dibandingkan dengan model terbaik."

msgctxt "RegressionLinearBayesian|"
msgid "All models are compared to the null model."
msgstr "Semua model dibandingkan dengan model null."

msgctxt "RegressionLinearBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Displays a plot of the marginal posterior distribution for each predictor."
msgstr ""
"Menampilkan diagram distribusi posterior margin untuk setiap prediktor."

msgctxt "RegressionLinearBayesian|"
msgid "Shows the relation between model fit and complexity."
msgstr "Menampilkan relasi antara kesesuaian dan kompleksitas model."

msgctxt "RegressionLinearBayesian|"
msgid "Displays the cumulative distribution function of the model search."
msgstr "Menampilkan fungsi distribusi kumulatif dari pencarian model."

msgctxt "RegressionLinearBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Displays a Q-Q plot of the model averaged predictions against the residuals."
msgstr "Menampilkan diagram Q-Q dari prediksi direrata model terhadap residu."

msgctxt "RegressionLinearBayesian|"
msgid "Compare models using the Akaike Information Criterion."
msgstr "Bandingkan model menggunakan Kriteria Informasi Akaike."

msgctxt "RegressionLinearBayesian|"
msgid "Uses the MLE of g from the marginal likelihood within each model."
msgstr "Menggunakan MLE g dari kemungkinan margin dalam setiap model."

msgctxt "RegressionLinearBayesian|"
msgid ""
"A mixture of g-priors where the prior on g/(1+g) is a Beta(1, alpha/2). This "
"uses the Cephes library for evaluation of the marginal likelihoods and may "
"be numerically unstable for large n or R2 close to 1. Default choice of "
"alpha is 3."
msgstr ""
"Campuran priori-g di mana priori pada g/(1+g) adalah Beta (1, alfa/2). Ini "
"menggunakan pustaka Cephes untuk evaluasi kemungkinan margin dan mungkin "
"secara numerik tidak stabil untuk n besar atau R2 dekat dengan 1. Pilihan "
"alfa bawaan adalah 3."

msgctxt "RegressionLinearBayesian|"
msgid ""
"A mixture of g-priors where u = g/n and u Beta(1, alpha/2) to provide "
"consistency when the null model is true."
msgstr ""
"Campuran dari priori-g di mana u = g/n dan u Beta(1, alfa/2) untuk "
"menyediakan konsistensi ketika model null benar."

msgctxt "RegressionLinearBayesian|"
msgid "Default Beta(a = 1, b = 1)."
msgstr "Beta bawaan(a = 1, b = 1)."

msgctxt "RegressionLinearBayesian|"
msgid "Uniform prior distribution."
msgstr "Gabungkan distribusi priori."

msgctxt "RegressionLinearBayesian|"
msgid "Bernoulli prior. Default p = 0.5."
msgstr "Priori Bernoulli. Bawaan p = 0.5."

msgctxt "RegressionLinearBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Samples with replacement via an MCMC algorithm that combines the birth/death "
"random walk with a random swap move to interchange a variable in the model. "
"No. samples indicates the number of MCMC samples to draw. Setting the value "
"to 0 implies the number of MCMC iterations is equal to 10 times the number "
"of models. Sampling stops when min(number of models, MCMC iterations) is "
"reached."
msgstr ""
"Sampel dengan penggantian melalui algoritma MCMC yang mengombinasikan jalan "
"acak kelahiran/kematian dengan pindah pertukaran acak untuk mengganti "
"variabel dalam model. Jml. sampel mengindikasikan jumlah sampel MCMC untuk "
"digambar. Mengatur nilai ke 0 berarti jumlah iterasi MCMC sama dengan 10 "
"kali jumlah model. Pensampelan menghentikan ketika min(jumlah model, iterasi "
"MCMC) tercapai."

msgctxt "RegressionLogistic|"
msgid "The weights used for weighted least squares regression."
msgstr "Berat digunakan untuk regresi kuadrat terlemah terberat."

msgctxt "RegressionLogistic|"
msgid ""
"Ticking this box will add a coefficient estimate of the intercept as well. "
"This corresponds to the first level for the independent variable."
msgstr ""
"Menyentang kotak ini akan menambahkan estimasi koefisien dari intersep juga. "
"Ini menyesuaikan dengan tingkat pertama untuk variabel independen."

msgctxt "RegressionLogistic|"
msgid ""
"Standardized estimates represent estimates where the predictors are "
"standardized (X-standardization)."
msgstr ""
"Estimasi terstandardisasi merepresentasikan estimasi di mana prediktor "
"distandardisasi (Standardisasi-X)."

msgctxt "RegressionLogistic|"
msgid ""
"Coverage of the confidence intervals in percentages. The default value is "
"95%, which can be changed by the user."
msgstr ""
"Cakupan interval kepercayaan dalam persentase. Nilai bawaan adalah 95%, yang "
"dapat diubah oleh pengguna."

msgctxt "RegressionLogistic|"
msgid ""
"This option controls for errors that are not independent and identically "
"distributed. The use of robust standard errors will not change the "
"coefficient estimates. If this option is not selected the normal standard "
"error will be computed."
msgstr ""
"Opsi ini mengontrol untuk galat yang tidak independen dan secara identik "
"distribusi. Penggunaan galat standar kekuatan tidak akan mengubah estimasi "
"koefisien. Jika opsi ini tidak dipilih galat standar normal akan dihitung."

msgctxt "RegressionLogistic|"
msgid ""
"Shows the maximum ratio of the likelihood of the obtained p value under H1 "
"vs the likelihood of the obtained p value under H0. For example, if the two-"
"sided p-value equals .05, the Vovk-Sellke MPR equals 2.46, indicating that "
"this p-value is at most 2.46 times more likely to occur under H1 than under "
"H0."
msgstr ""
"Menampilkan rasio maksimum dari kemungkinan nilai p terambil di bawah H1 vs "
"nilai p terambil di bawah H0. Contohnya, jika nilai-p dua sisi sama "
"dengan .05, MPR Vovk-Sellke sama dengan 2.46, mengindikasikan bahwa nilai-p "
"ini kemungkinan lebih banyak 2.46 kali lebih besar terjadi di bawah H1 dari "
"di bawah H0."

msgctxt "RegressionLogistic|"
msgid ""
"Displays Tolerance and Variance Inflation Factor for each predictor in the "
"model to assess multicollinearity."
msgstr ""
"Menampilkan Faktor Inflasi Toleransi dan Varians untuk setiap prediktor di "
"model untuk mengevaluasi multikolinearitas."

msgctxt "RegressionLogistic|"
msgid "How often the model's prediction match the actual outcomes."
msgstr "Seberapa sering prediksi model cocok hasil aktual."

msgctxt "RegressionLogistic|"
msgid ""
"The F-measure is based on the amount of systematic variance divided by the "
"amount of unsystematic variance i.e., mean squares for the model / the "
"residual mean squares."
msgstr ""
"Pengukuran-F berdasarkan jumlah varians sistematis dibagikan dengan jumlah "
"varians tidak sistematis yaitu, rerata kuadrat untuk model / rerata kuadrat "
"residu."

msgctxt "RegressionLogistic|"
msgid ""
"Displays the specified confidence interval around the regression line on the "
"plot."
msgstr ""
"Menampilkan interval kepercayaan dispesifikasikan dikelilingi garis regresi "
"pada diagram."

msgctxt "RegressionLogistic|"
msgid "Displays individual data points on the plot."
msgstr "Menampilkan titik data individu pada diagram."

msgctxt "RegressionLogistic|"
msgid ""
"If the assumptions of the linear regression model hold, then these residuals "
"should scatter randomly about a horizontal line. Any systematic pattern or "
"clustering of the residuals suggests model assumption violations."
msgstr ""
"Jika asumsi model regresi linear ditahan, kemudian residu ini harus bercak "
"secara acak tentang garis horizontal. Pola sistematis atau klaster apa pun "
"dari residu menyarankan pelanggaran asumsi model."

msgctxt "RegressionLogistic|"
msgid "Adds every two-way interaction."
msgstr "Menambahkan setiap interaksi dua arah."

msgctxt "RegressionLogistic|"
msgid ""
"Plots predicted probabilities on the logit scale, to ensure a linear "
"relation."
msgstr ""
"Mendiagramkan probabilitas terprediksi pada skala logit, untuk memastikan "
"relasi linear."

msgctxt "RegressionLogistic|"
msgid "The standardized deviance residuals."
msgstr "Residu devians terstandardisasi."

msgctxt "RegressionLogistic|"
msgid ""
"Plots performance of the model by plotting the true positive rate to the "
"false positive rate. The cutoff step determines the threshold at which an "
"observation is classified as positive or a negative."
msgstr ""
"Mendiagramkan kinerja model dengan mendiagramkan tingkat positif benar atau "
"tingkat positif palsu. Langkah pemotongan menentukan ambang batas di mana "
"observasi diklasifikasikan sebagai positif atau negatif."

msgctxt "RegressionLogistic|"
msgid ""
"By clicking this box, the specified cutoff step is displayed on the "
"performance plot."
msgstr ""
"Dengan mengeklik kotak ini, langkah pemotongan dispesifikasikan ditampilkan "
"pada diagram kinerja."

msgctxt "RegressionLogistic|"
msgid ""
"Displays the Positive predicitve value on the y axis vs the true positive "
"rate/sensitivity on the x axis. Useful for imbalanced datasets. The cutoff "
"step determines the threshold at which an observation is classified as "
"positive or negative. "
msgstr ""
"Menampilkan nilai prediktif Positif pada sumbu y vs tingkat/sensitifitas "
"positif benar pada sumbu x. Berguna untuk rangkaian data tidak seimbang. "
"Langkah pemotongan menentukan ambang batas di mana observasi "
"diklasifikasikan sebagai positif atau negatif. "

msgctxt "RegressionLogistic|"
msgid ""
"By clicking this box, the specified cutoff step is displayed on the "
"precision recall plot."
msgstr ""
"Dengan mengeklik kotak ini, langkah pemotongan dispesifikasikan ditampilkan "
"pada diagram recall presisi."

msgctxt "RegressionLogisticBayesian|"
msgid ""
"The Bayesian Logistic Regression allows you to model a linear relationship "
"between one or more explanatory variable/s and a categorical dependent "
"variable.\n"
msgstr ""
"Regresi Logistik Bayes mengizinkan Anda untuk memodelkan hubungan linear "
"antara satu atau lebih variabel penjelasan dan variabel dependen "
"kategorikal.\n"

msgctxt "RegressionLogisticBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Drag the variables that are covariates to this box. Covariates are "
"continuous variables that have an influence on the dependent variable but "
"are not part of the experimental manipulation."
msgstr ""
"Seretkan variabel yang kovariat ke kotak ini. Kovariat adalah variabel "
"berkelanjutan yang memiliki influens pada variabel dependen tetapi bukan "
"bagian dari manipulasi eksperimental."

msgctxt "RegressionLogisticBayesian|"
msgid "The weights used for weighted least squares regression."
msgstr "Berat digunakan untuk regresi kuadrat terlemah terberat."

msgctxt "RegressionLogisticBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Output table containing the Marginal Posterior Summaries of Coefficients."
msgstr "Tabel luaran berisi Ringkasan Posterior Margin Koefisien."

msgctxt "RegressionLogisticBayesian|"
msgid "Compares across all models."
msgstr "Membandingkan di seluruh model."

msgctxt "RegressionLogisticBayesian|"
msgid "Compares across matched models."
msgstr "Membandingkan di seluruh model cocok."

msgctxt "RegressionLogisticBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Displays a plot of the most likely values of the effect size for each model "
"with their corresponding credible intervals."
msgstr ""
"Menampilkan diagram nilai paling memungkinkan dari ukuran efek untuk setiap "
"model dengan interval kredibel sesuai dengan mereka."

msgctxt "RegressionLogisticBayesian|"
msgid "By clicking this box, the intercept is omitted from the plot."
msgstr "Dengan mengeklik kotak ini, intersep dihilangkan dari diagram."

msgctxt "RegressionLogisticBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Displays the most complex model, meaning the model which includes all the "
"predictors."
msgstr ""
"Menampilkan model paling kompleks, artinya model mana menyertakan semua "
"prediktor."

msgctxt "RegressionLogisticBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Displays the median model, meaning the smallest model in which all the "
"predictors are more likely to be part of the true model than not given the "
"data. i.e., have a posterior inclusion probability equal or greater than 0.5."
msgstr ""
"Menampilkan model median, artinya model terkecil di mana semua prediktor "
"lebih mungkin bagian dari model benar dari pada data tidak diberikan. Yaitu, "
"memiliki probabilitas inklusi posterior sama atau lebih dari 0.5."

msgctxt "RegressionLogisticBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Displays the model in which the predictor coefficients are averaged out "
"across all models."
msgstr ""
"Menampilkan model di mana koefisien prediktor direratakan di seluruh model."

msgctxt "RegressionLogisticBayesian|"
msgid "Compares each model against the model selected here."
msgstr "Membandingkan setiap model melawan model dipilih di sini."

msgctxt "RegressionLogisticBayesian|"
msgid "All models are compared to the best model."
msgstr "Semua model dibandingkan dengan model terbaik."

msgctxt "RegressionLogisticBayesian|"
msgid "All models are compared to the null model."
msgstr "Semua model dibandingkan dengan model null."

msgctxt "RegressionLogisticBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Displays a plot of the marginal posterior distribution for each predictor."
msgstr ""
"Menampilkan diagram distribusi posterior margin untuk setiap prediktor."

msgctxt "RegressionLogisticBayesian|"
msgid "Shows the relation between model fit and complexity."
msgstr "Menampilkan relasi antara kesesuaian dan kompleksitas model."

msgctxt "RegressionLogisticBayesian|"
msgid "Displays the cumulative distribution function of the model search."
msgstr "Menampilkan fungsi distribusi kumulatif dari pencarian model."

msgctxt "RegressionLogisticBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Displays a Q-Q plot of the model averaged predictions against the residuals."
msgstr "Menampilkan diagram Q-Q dari prediksi direrata model terhadap residu."

msgctxt "RegressionLogisticBayesian|"
msgid "Compare models using the Akaike Information Criterion."
msgstr "Bandingkan model menggunakan Kriteria Informasi Akaike."

msgctxt "RegressionLogisticBayesian|"
msgid "Uses the MLE of g from the marginal likelihood within each model."
msgstr "Menggunakan MLE g dari kemungkinan margin dalam setiap model."

msgctxt "RegressionLogisticBayesian|"
msgid "Zellner's g-prior. There is an option to adjust the alpha parameter."
msgstr "Priori-g Zellner. Ada opsi untuk menyesuaikan parameter alfa."

msgctxt "RegressionLogisticBayesian|"
msgid "Default Beta(a = 1, b = 1)."
msgstr "Beta bawaan(a = 1, b = 1)."

msgctxt "RegressionLogisticBayesian|"
msgid "Uniform prior distribution."
msgstr "Gabungkan distribusi priori."

msgctxt "RegressionLogisticBayesian|"
msgid "Bernoulli prior. Default p = 0.5."
msgstr "Priori Bernoulli. Bawaan p = 0.5."

msgctxt "RegressionLogisticBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Samples with replacement via an MCMC algorithm that combines the birth/death "
"random walk with a random swap move to interchange a variable in the model. "
"No. samples indicates the number of MCMC samples to draw. Setting the value "
"to 0 implies the number of MCMC iterations is equal to 10 times the number "
"of models. Sampling stops when min(number of models, MCMC iterations) is "
"reached."
msgstr ""
"Sampel dengan penggantian melalui algoritma MCMC yang mengombinasikan jalan "
"acak kelahiran/kematian dengan pindah pertukaran acak untuk mengganti "
"variabel dalam model. Jml. sampel mengindikasikan jumlah sampel MCMC untuk "
"digambar. Mengatur nilai ke 0 berarti jumlah iterasi MCMC sama dengan 10 "
"kali jumlah model. Pensampelan menghentikan ketika min(jumlah model, iterasi "
"MCMC) tercapai."

msgctxt "RegressionLinear|"
msgid "Include quadratic terms"
msgstr "Sertakan istilah kuadratik"

msgctxt "RegressionLinear|"
msgid "Include quadratic terms for the covariates in each model."
msgstr "Sertakan istilah kuadratik untuk kovariat di setiap model."

msgctxt "RegressionLinear|"
msgid "Regression equation"
msgstr "Persamaan regresi"

msgctxt "RegressionLinear|"
msgid "Displays regression equations for each model."
msgstr "Menampilkan persamaan regresi untuk setiap model."

msgctxt "RegressionLogistic|"
msgid "Include quadratic terms"
msgstr "Sertakan istilah kuadratik"

msgctxt "RegressionLogistic|"
msgid "Include quadratic terms for the covariates in each model."
msgstr "Sertakan istilah kuadratik untuk kovariat di setiap model."

msgctxt "Correlation|"
msgid ""
"Displays scatter plots for all variable pairs. In a matrix format, these are "
"placed above the diagonal. For partial correlations, plots show the "
"relationship between X and Y after removing the effect of Z, and axes then "
"represent residuals from regressing X and Y on Z."
msgstr ""
"Menampilkan diagram pencaran untuk semua pasangan variabel. Dalam format "
"matriks, ini ditempatkan di atas diagonal. Untuk korelasi parsial, diagram "
"menampilkan hubungan antara X dan Y setelah menghapus efek Z, dan sumbu "
"kemudian merepresentasikan residu dari meregresi X dan Y pada Z."

msgctxt "Correlation|"
msgid ""
"Display histogram and the corresponding density plot for each variable. In a "
"matrix format, these are placed on the diagonal"
msgstr ""
"Tampilkan histogram dan diagram kepadatan yang sesuai untuk setiap variabel. "
"Dalam format matriks, ini ditempatkan pada diagonal"

msgctxt "RegressionLinear|"
msgid ""
"Specify the method for entering predictors into the model. For the Enter "
"method, predictors are added as specified in the Model tab. With Forward, "
"Backward, or Stepwise methods, predictors listed in Model 1 are treated as "
"candidate variables that can be added to or removed from the model based on "
"statistical criteria (found under Method Specification). Predictors listed "
"in Model 0 are forced into the model and remain in all steps, regardless of "
"their fit."
msgstr ""
"Tentukan metode untuk memasukkan prediktor ke dalam model. Untuk metode "
"Masukkan, prediktor ditambahkan sebagai ditentukan di tab Model. Dengan "
"metode Maju, Mundur, atau Bertahap, prediktor didaftar di Model 1 "
"diperlakukan sebagai variabel kandidat yang dapat ditambahkan ke atau "
"dihapus dari model berdasarkan kriteria statistik (ditemukan di bawah "
"Spesifikasi Metode). Prediktor didaftar di Model 0 dipaksakan ke dalam model "
"dan tetap di semua langkah, terlepas dari penyesuaian mereka."

msgctxt "RegressionLinear|"
msgid ""
"All predictors are entered into the models as specified in the Model tab."
msgstr ""
"Semua prediktor dimasukkan ke dalam model sebagai ditentukan di tab Model."

msgctxt "RegressionLinear|"
msgid ""
"Displays Q-Q plot of the standardized residuals. The confidence band shows "
"the expected range of residuals under normality; points outside the band "
"suggest deviations from normality."
msgstr ""
"Menampilkan diagram Q-Q residu terstandardisasi. Rentang kepercayaan "
"menampilkan rentang terharap residu dalam normalitas; titik di luar rentang "
"menyarankan deviasi dari normalitas."

msgctxt "RegressionLinear|"
msgid "Confidence interval"
msgstr "Interval kepercayaan"

msgctxt "RegressionLogistic|"
msgid ""
"Specify the method for entering predictors into the model. For the Enter "
"method, predictors are added as specified in the Model tab. With Forward, "
"Backward, or Stepwise methods, predictors assigned to Model 1 are treated as "
"candidate variables that can be added to or removed from the model based on "
"AIC. Predictors assigned to Model 0 are forced into the model and remain in "
"all steps, regardless of AIC."
msgstr ""
"Tentukan metode untuk memasukkan prediktor ke dalam model. Untuk metode "
"Masukkan, prediktor ditambahkan sebagai ditentukan di tab Model. Dengan "
"metode Maju, Mundur, atau Bertahap, prediktor ditugaskan ke Model 1 "
"diperlakukan sebagai variabel kandidat yang dapat ditambahkan ke atau "
"dihapus dari model berdasarkan AIC. Prediktor ditugaskan ke Model 0 "
"dipaksakan ke dalam model dan tetap di semua langkah, terlepas dari AIC."

msgctxt "RegressionLogistic|"
msgid ""
"All predictors are entered into the models as specified in the Model tab."
msgstr ""
"Semua prediktor dimasukkan ke dalam model sebagai ditentukan di tab Model."

msgctxt "RegressionLogistic|"
msgid ""
"All predictors are entered simultaneously, and then removed sequentially "
"based on AIC."
msgstr ""
"Semua prediktor dimasukkan secara bersamaan, dan kemudian dihapus secara "
"sekuensial berdasarkan AIC."

msgctxt "RegressionLogistic|"
msgid "Predictors are entered sequentially based on AIC."
msgstr "Prediktor dimasukkan secara sekuensial berdasarkan AIC."

msgctxt "RegressionLogistic|"
msgid ""
"Predictors are entered sequentially based on AIC; after each step, the least "
"useful predictor is removed."
msgstr ""
"Prediktor dimasukkan secara sekuensial berdasarkan AIC; setelah setiap "
"langkah, prediktor paling tidak berguna dihilangkan."

msgctxt "RegressionLogistic|"
msgid ""
"Continuous predictor variable(s). If ordinal variables are entered it is "
"assumed that their levels are equidistant. Hence, ordinal variables are "
"treated as continuous predictor variables."
msgstr ""
"Variabel prediktor kontinu. Jika variabel ordinal dimasukkan diasumsikan "
"bahwa tingkat mereka berjarak sama. Oleh karena itu, variabel ordinal "
"diperlakukan sebagai variabel prediktor kontinu."

msgctxt "RegressionLogistic|"
msgid ""
"Categorical predictor variable(s). Ordinal variables here are treated as "
"categorical predictor variables, thus, the ordinal information is ignored."
msgstr ""
"Variabel prediktor kategorikal. Variabel ordinal di sini diperlakukan "
"sebagai nilai prediktor kategorikal, sehingga, informasi ordinal diabaikan."

